= Reverse (a.k.a. "esrever") =

 * Una humilde funcion para dar vuelta los caracteres usando Python, letras o numeros, ejemplo simple.

{{{
#!code python

#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*- 
def reverse(this):
    return ' '.join(''.join(list(things)[::-1]) for things in this.split())
inputz = raw_input()
print reverse(inputz)
}}}

